scenes.description: The holoro members discuss the gauge and prepare for the next question.
Ollie presents the 5th question about an animal attack during her stream. Reine correctly answers 'cockroach'.
Anya presents the 6th question about her performance at hololive 4th fes. Ollie correctly answers 'cutlery'.

subtitles.original: Iya, kalau misalnya ini...
subtitles.english: Yeah, if for example this...

subtitles.original: Pokoknya gitu deh. BTW, apakah dia akan naik menurut kalian?
subtitles.english: Anyway, that's it. BTW, do you think it'll go up?

subtitles.original: Lho! Kok turun! Kok turun!
subtitles.english: Wait! Why is it going down! It's going down!

subtitles.original: Yah, Ollie salah!
subtitles.english: Aw, Ollie was wrong!

subtitles.original: Ollie salah!
subtitles.english: Ollie was wrong!

subtitles.original: Wah, Ollie salah! Parah banget, aku kira dia bener.
subtitles.english: Whoa, Ollie was wrong! That's too bad, I thought she was right.

subtitles.original: Gimana sih? Yah!
subtitles.english: What happened? Aw!

subtitles.original: Wah, dia jatuh! Dia jatuh!
subtitles.english: Whoa, she's falling! She's falling!

subtitles.original: Oke, aduh maaf, maaf gelut.
subtitles.english: Okay, sorry, sorry for the fight.

subtitles.original: Belum selesai! Nanti, nanti, nanti.
subtitles.english: It's not over yet! Later, later, later.

subtitles.original: Gelutnya di belakang parkiran saja kalau sudah selesai.
subtitles.english: Just fight behind the parking lot once we're done.

subtitles.original: Di belakang parkiran? Tidak ramah bintang satu.
subtitles.english: Behind the parking lot? One star review, not friendly.

subtitles.original: Serem banget tante. Tapi kita masih bisa nggak sih?
subtitles.english: That's scary, auntie. But can we still do it?

subtitles.original: Masih bisa lah menurutku. Bisa, bisa, bisa lah.
subtitles.english: I think we still can. We can, we can, for sure.

subtitles.original: Oke. Sampai penuh.
subtitles.english: Okay. Until it's full.

subtitles.original: Sampai penuh. Sampai ke pertanyaan...
subtitles.english: Until it's full. Until the next...

subtitles.original: ...berikutnya!
subtitles.english: ...question!

subtitles.original: Wah, kalau gitu waktunya untuk pertanyaan selanjutnya nggak sih?
subtitles.english: Whoa, then isn't it time for the next question?

subtitles.original: Waktunya untuk pertanyaan selanjutnya!
subtitles.english: Time for the next question!

subtitles.original: Aku deh! Aku deh!
subtitles.english: Me! Let me do it!

subtitles.original: Aku! Aku mau nanya! Aku mau nanya!
subtitles.english: Me! I want to ask! I want to ask!

subtitles.original: Silakan Ollie. Silakan Ollie.
subtitles.english: Go ahead, Ollie. Go ahead, Ollie.

subtitles.original: Kalau begitu kita langsung masuk saja, pertanyaan...
subtitles.english: Then let's just jump right in, the next...

subtitles.original: ...berikutnya!
subtitles.english: ...question!

subtitles.original: Binatang apa yang menyerang Ollie saat stream?
subtitles.english: What animal attacked Ollie during a stream?

subtitles.original: Binatang apa yang menyerang Ollie saat stream?
subtitles.english: What animal attacked Ollie during a stream?

subtitles.original: Apakah laba-laba, A, atau B, kecoak?
subtitles.english: Is it a spider, A, or B, a cockroach?

subtitles.original: Siapa nih mau jawab? Reine mau jawab?
subtitles.english: Who wants to answer? Does Reine want to?

subtitles.original: Aku! Gantian kamu yang jatuh!
subtitles.english: Me! It's your turn to fall!

subtitles.original: Gantian kamu yang jatuh! Aduh.
subtitles.english: It's your turn to fall! Oh boy.

subtitles.original: Binatang yang menyerang Ollie saat stream...
subtitles.english: The animal that attacked Ollie during a stream...

subtitles.original: Kayaknya... aku tahu nih, aku tahu.
subtitles.english: I think... I know this, I know.

subtitles.original: Laba-laba itu serem, tapi dia nggak loncat. Biasanya pelan.
subtitles.english: Spiders are scary, but they don't jump. Usually they're slow.

subtitles.original: Jadi kalau kecoak itu kan biasanya kayak "werrr" gitu.
subtitles.english: But cockroaches usually go "werrr" like that.

subtitles.original: Iya, soalnya wording-nya "menyerang".
subtitles.english: Yeah, because the wording is "attacked".

subtitles.original: Jadi instingku, aku akan menjawab B, kecoak. B!
subtitles.english: So my instinct says I'll answer B, cockroach. B!

subtitles.original: Wah, kayaknya percaya diri.
subtitles.english: Whoa, someone's confident.

subtitles.original: Kalau begitu, B mulu ya dari tadi kayaknya.
subtitles.english: It seems like it's been B every time.

subtitles.original: Oke, kalau begitu aku akan maju ke B, oke?
subtitles.english: Okay, then I'll head for B, okay?

subtitles.original: Oke! Ayo bersiap!
subtitles.english: Okay! Get ready!

subtitles.original: Tiga, dua, satu!
subtitles.english: Three, two, one!

subtitles.original: Wah! Yeay!
subtitles.english: Whoa! Yay!

subtitles.original: Wah, selamat! Bagus sekali!
subtitles.english: Wow, congrats! That was great!

subtitles.original: Okaeri! Yeay!
subtitles.english: Welcome back! Yay!

subtitles.original: Ayo, ayo! Naik, naik, naik!
subtitles.english: Come on, come on! Go up, go up, go up!

subtitles.original: Naik, naik, naik!
subtitles.english: Go up, go up, go up!

subtitles.original: Naik! Kamu kapan diserang kecoak?
subtitles.english: Go up! When did you get attacked by a cockroach?

subtitles.original: Pernah waktu itu, awal-awal debut, tiba-tiba ada kecoak melayang gitu.
subtitles.english: It happened once, during early debut, suddenly a cockroach was flying around.

subtitles.original: Pancuran Ollie kali itu.
subtitles.english: That was Ollie's "pancuran".

subtitles.original: Zom-ray! Zom-ray! Ternyata...
subtitles.english: Zom-ray! Zom-ray! Turns out...

subtitles.original: ...zom-ray pun ini ya, cross species juga.
subtitles.english: ...the zom-ray is cross-species too.

subtitles.original: Cross species, betul! Halus sekali!
subtitles.english: Cross-species, exactly! Very smooth!

subtitles.original: Wah keren! Masih belum, masih aman.
subtitles.english: Whoa, cool! Not yet, still safe.

subtitles.original: Masih belum jatuh, guys. Kita harus memenuhi gauge ini sampai maks.
subtitles.english: Still haven't fallen, guys. We need to fill this gauge to the max.

subtitles.original: Mentok! Kalau begitu langsung saja kita ke pertanyaan...
subtitles.english: To the limit! Then let's head straight to the next...

subtitles.original: ...selanjutnya!
subtitles.english: ...question!

subtitles.original: Wah sip! Ini sudah berapa? Keenam ya?
subtitles.english: Alright! How many is this? The sixth?

subtitles.original: Pertanyaan keenam! Wah, cepat sekali ya.
subtitles.english: The sixth question! Wow, that was fast.

subtitles.original: Cepat sekali. Kalau gitu siapa yang mau nanya?
subtitles.english: Very fast. Then who wants to ask?

subtitles.original: Kalau gitu aku deh! Giliran aku yang nanya ya guys.
subtitles.english: Then let it be me! It's my turn to ask, guys.

subtitles.original: Oke, oke. Oke, pertanyaan keenam!
subtitles.english: Okay, okay. Okay, the sixth question!

subtitles.original: Apa judul lagu yang dinyanyikan Anya pada hololive 4th fes. Our Bright Parade?
subtitles.english: What is the title of the song Anya sang at hololive 4th fes. Our Bright Parade?

subtitles.original: Apa judul lagu yang dinyanyikan aku pada hololive 4th fes. Our Bright Parade?
subtitles.english: What's the title of the song I sang at hololive 4th fes. Our Bright Parade?

subtitles.original: Masa nggak nonton? A, Phony, B, cutlery?
subtitles.english: Don't tell me you didn't watch? A, Phony, B, cutlery?

subtitles.original: Wah! Aku tahu! Aku tahu! Aku tahu!
subtitles.english: Whoa! I know! I know! I know!

subtitles.original: Jawab! Jawab!
subtitles.english: Answer! Answer!

subtitles.original: Jawab B, cutlery!
subtitles.english: Answer B, cutlery!

subtitles.original: Apakah sudah yakin? Saya yakin!
subtitles.english: Are you sure? I'm sure!

subtitles.original: Oke Kureiji Ollie, silakan kamu lari.
subtitles.english: Okay Kureiji Ollie, please run.

subtitles.original: Oke! Huisha!
subtitles.english: Okay! Huisha!

subtitles.original: Wah! Posisi siap! Siap!
subtitles.english: Whoa! Ready position! Ready!

subtitles.original: Tiga, dua, satu, go!
subtitles.english: Three, two, one, go!

subtitles.original: Wah! Yeay!
subtitles.english: Whoa! Yay!

subtitles.original: Keren kan? Sudah saya hafal semua.
subtitles.english: Cool, right? I've memorized them all.

subtitles.original: Keren banget! Semua yang tampil di fes aku hafal semua.
subtitles.english: So cool! I've memorized everyone who performed at the fes.

subtitles.original: Iya, dia paling sering nonton ya konser-konser Hololive dan lain-lain.
subtitles.english: Yeah, she watches Hololive concerts and stuff the most.

subtitles.original: Kalian semua juga nonton kan? Iya!
subtitles.english: You all watch them too, right? Yeah!

subtitles.original: Berarti gauge-nya naik dong! Naik lagi, naik lagi!
subtitles.english: That means the gauge goes up! Up again, up again!

subtitles.original: Naik lagi! Wah, dikit lagi!
subtitles.english: Up again! Whoa, just a bit more!

subtitles.original: Gampang banget ya dari tadi? Kecurang! Kecurang!
subtitles.english: It's been so easy, right? Cheating! Cheating!

subtitles.original: Naik lagi dong, please! Kok cuma segitu? Ya sudahlah.
subtitles.english: Go up more, please! Why only that much? Oh well.

subtitles.original: Ya sudah, kita tinggal berusaha...
subtitles.english: Alright, we just need to try...

subtitles.original: Lho, lho, lho! Berhenti! Naik atau turun?
subtitles.english: Wait, wait, wait! It stopped! Up or down?

subtitles.original: Naik lagi dikit, dikit lagi, dikit lagi.
subtitles.english: Up a bit more, just a bit more, just a bit more.

subtitles.original: Bisa dinaikin nggak sampai mentok?
subtitles.english: Can we push it to the limit?

subtitles.original: Dikit lagi! Ya ampun! Yah! Yah! Yah!
subtitles.english: Just a bit more! My gosh! Aw! Aw! Aw!

subtitles.original: Mohon maaf, maaf.
subtitles.english: Sorry, sorry.

subtitles.original: Oke kalau gitu, kita pengen memenuhi ini kan?
subtitles.english: Okay then, we want to fill this up, right?

subtitles.original: Kalau begitu langsung aja nggak sih ke pertanyaan berikutnya!
subtitles.english: Then let's just go straight to the next question!

subtitles.original: Dikit lagi nih guys. Udah ke berapa? Ketujuh?
subtitles.english: Just a bit more, guys. Which one is it? The seventh?

subtitles.original: Pertanyaan ketujuh? Wah!
subtitles.english: The seventh question? Wow!

subtitles.original: Cepat sekali!
subtitles.english: So fast!
